{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0e81969298","title":"“统购统销搞糟了”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f917c39459","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0e81969298"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3c8ddc4342","name":"刘伯奇"},{"id":"4912cadfa8","name":"王豪"},{"id":"4fac142a8e","name":"姚鸿烈"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"cd6d1d2c70","name":"李燕吉"},{"id":"efb38951a2","name":"程月华"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"848bce9fa3","type":"title","text":"“统购统销搞糟了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"755ceea056","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院王豪姚鸿烈刘伯奇程月华李燕吉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"248cd80af4","type":"appellation","text":"王豪说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"1f66a5e37a","type":"appellation","text":"「历史上的战争有两种类型，一是民族战争，一是农民战争。统购统销扣的太紧，可能有局部的，少数的农民骚动。统购统销搞糟了，在农村中买的不是余粮而是口粮。使农民挨饿了，农民都想把干部干掉。粮食出口太多，城市猪肉，油……等等都买不到。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"41c0150c19","type":"appellation","text":"姚鸿烈说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"928925f193","type":"appellation","text":"「统购统销的错误很大，这个错误不仅在下面，而且在中央也有，每个地方都搞糟了，换言之方针错了。为什么中央有错，因为上面不错，下面会错，所以中央不能有许多错。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"3048c7c8c9","type":"appellation","text":"刘伯奇说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"e7d9562ab3","type":"appellation","text":"「统购之后，农民买不到粮食。」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"2a1b7b289d","type":"paragraph","text":"对乡村人口不能流入城市政策，他认为是「现在社会职业不自由，宪法规定没保障。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"01525a01a8","type":"paragraph","text":"「合作化后，没零钱化，现在地都入社了，小菜园也入社了，小孩有病没钱医治，政策不解决实际问题。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"2c692d0786","type":"appellation","text":"程月华说：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"c4ff7daf12","type":"appellation","text":"「统购统销时，我们那儿就是没有吃的。」","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"815274e67a","type":"appellation","text":"李燕吉说：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"af34d771c7","type":"appellation","text":"「统购统销搞糟了，粮食定量很不好，又回复到国民党时代的购粮状态中去了。五六年以来城市副食品少了，是国家出口给苏联和人民民主国家去了。」","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"},{"id":"0f4218c123","type":"paragraph","text":"「农民生活还不如工人生活好，工资制度不合理，体力劳动与脑力劳动相差不多。」","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298"}],"page":{"id":"619fcf1149","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0e81969298","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}